graph TB
    subgraph "Training Operator Component"
        Controller[Training Operator<br/>Controller Manager]
        PyTorchCtrl[PyTorchJob Controller]
        TFCtrl[TFJob Controller]
        MPICtrl[MPIJob Controller]
        XGBoostCtrl[XGBoostJob Controller]
        JAXCtrl[JAXJob Controller]
        PaddleCtrl[PaddleJob Controller]
        Webhook[Validation Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]

        Controller -->|manages| PyTorchCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| TFCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| MPICtrl
        Controller -->|manages| XGBoostCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| JAXCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| PaddleCtrl
        Controller -->|serves| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PyTorchJobCR[PyTorchJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        TFJobCR[TFJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MPIJobCR[MPIJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        XGBoostJobCR[XGBoostJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        JAXJobCR[JAXJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        PaddleJobCR[PaddleJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Pods[Training Pods<br/>Master/Workers]
        Services[Headless Services<br/>23456/TCP]
        PodGroups[PodGroups<br/>Gang Scheduling]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates via kubectl/SDK| PyTorchJobCR
    User -->|creates via kubectl/SDK| TFJobCR
    User -->|creates via kubectl/SDK| MPIJobCR
    User -->|creates via kubectl/SDK| XGBoostJobCR

    PyTorchJobCR -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJobCR -->|watched by| TFCtrl
    MPIJobCR -->|watched by| MPICtrl
    XGBoostJobCR -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    JAXJobCR -->|watched by| JAXCtrl
    PaddleJobCR -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl

    PyTorchJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook
    TFJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook
    MPIJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook
    XGBoostJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook
    JAXJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook
    PaddleJobCR -.->|validates| Webhook

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    TFCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    MPICtrl -->|creates| Pods
    XGBoostCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    JAXCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    PaddleCtrl -->|creates| Pods

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services
    TFCtrl -->|creates| Services
    MPICtrl -->|creates| Services

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| PodGroups
    TFCtrl -->|creates| PodGroups
    MPICtrl -->|creates| PodGroups

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>Optional Gang Scheduling]
        SchedulerPlugins[Scheduler Plugins<br/>Optional Gang Scheduling]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/manages| K8sAPI
    Controller -.->|uses| Volcano
    Controller -.->|uses| SchedulerPlugins
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| Controller

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ODHOperator[OpenDataHub Operator]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    end

    ODHOperator -->|deploys| Controller
    Dashboard -->|UI management| Controller

